full_text: Screened by NARA, 6/1/2023 OMB No. 1615-0052; Expires 01/31/11 Department of Homeland Security N-400 Application U.S Citizenship and Immigration Services for Naturalization Print clearly or type your answers using CAPITAL letters. Failure to print clearly may delay your application. Use black ink. Part 1. Your Name (Person applying for naturalization) Write your USCIS A-Number here: A 026-271-163 A. Your current legal name. If "Yes," print the new name you would like to use. Do not use initials or abbreviations when writing your new name.
